OL,6,     FJaguar 2+2 E Type: Paul's on a big
OL,7,     Fday out collecting a 1971 Jaguar
OL,8,     FE-Type and a 1933 Morgan 3-wheeler
OL,9,     FSupersport but first there's a
OL,10,     Fflock of 300 chickens to negotiate
OL,11,     Fbefore he can load up.
OL,12,G2300 Bangers & Cash
OL,13,     FSubaru Impreza: Dave's in fast car
OL,14,     Fheaven as he picks up a rare
OL,15,     FSubaru Impreza and an equally
OL,16,     Fpowerful Ford Escort RS Cosworth
OL,17,     Ffrom North Wales.
