OL,12,G0100 Find It, Fix It, Flog It
OL,13,     FNew. Henry Cole refurbishes a
OL,14,     Fclassic Ford Mustang and a neon
OL,15,     Fgarage sign, while Simon O'Brien
OL,16,     Frestores a classic Chopper bicycle
OL,17,     Fand turns a bass guitar into a
